Greetings to the ECO community and its recognized leaders: @Andy | Eco @Hen | Eco @Henry  |  Eco @Dave | Eco and others. 
I saw Andy's post that it would be cool to create a real banner with the ECO logo on the streets of the city. 

However, virtual worlds are also a reality, and especially in times of quarantine. I came up with the idea to create my own ECO office for the community, in the most popular decentralized world - Decentraland.

A plot of land purchased for real money gives the owner the right to build anything on it. Now I want to show you what I did. All this works now. 

https://play.decentraland.org/?position=7,144

You can follow the link and see all the details yourself, all you need is a metamask. And for those who can't join right now, a short tour from me.

From a distance, the main entrance looks like this
And here is the side view
Behind you can see how the windows are lit advertising banners!
Once inside on the ground floor, you will find a patio, a lounge area.
And on the second floor, there is a working area, here you can see all the necessary links
On the right are the project leaders! Sorry I couldn't fit everyone in. I know that every member of the team is very valuable. Pay attention to the parrot. He talks too much
Tired? You can relax on the sofa.
From the office window, there is an amazing view.
And someone built a barbecue area nearby, I think he would not mind if we sometimes come to him 🙂

Well, that's the end of the tour. I hope you enjoyed it. However, it is better to see everything live, with your own eyes, because all you need is just a metamask and a link click :eco_backhand_down:. In the office you will find good music.
https://play.decentraland.org/?position=7,144
P.S. To get to the second floor, you need to jump up the stairs (space)
